    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_9_722-738",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "722-738",
      "markText": "像这个样子着陆可不雅观。”他说。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=722&rangeEnd=738",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=722&rangeEnd=738"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_18_2577-2617",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2577-2617",
      "markText": "“我常常跟我这位哥儿们讲，也应该生个海鸥宝宝，对不对，老兄？”其中一只大声宣称。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2577&rangeEnd=2617",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2577&rangeEnd=2617"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_7_757-780",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "757-780",
      "markText": "决定带些什么去度假，又留些什么在家里真的很难。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=780",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=780"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_7_1098-1161",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1098-1161",
      "markText": "“他是一个好小伙，”猫咪想着，嘴里塞得鼓鼓的，“他不仅仅是个好小伙，他是最棒的小伙子！”他一边改口，一边把嘴里的东西咽了下去。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1098&rangeEnd=1161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1098&rangeEnd=1161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_8_2582-2621",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2582-2621",
      "markText": "她的翅膀越来越沉，扇得也越来越慢。她的体力逐渐不支，已经没有原先飞得那么高了。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2582&rangeEnd=2621",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2582&rangeEnd=2621"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_11_2438-2475",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2438-2475",
      "markText": "他就这样一直瞪着对方，直到马蒂阿斯再也忍不住眨了眨眼睛，眼里都溢出泪来了。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_24_1945-2000",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "1945-2000",
      "markText": "“也许他并不懂得如何用鸟的翅膀去飞翔，可每当听他吟诵的时候，我总觉得他在凭借那些诗句畅游天空。”索尔巴斯回答。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300132898&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1945&rangeEnd=2000",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d3332130813ab9a69g018786?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1945&rangeEnd=2000"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300132898_20_1741-1776",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1741-1776",
      "markText": "有时我也会问自己，有人是不是发疯了，因为他们打算把海洋变成一个大垃圾场",
